These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, drama
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter
1. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the architect is the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | crime | disaster |
| Job    | engineer    | firefighter | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, cabbage, garlic
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food       | cabbage | garlic | grapefruit |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, scientist, software-developer
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the analyst##1
2. the scientist is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | photography | baking |
| Job   | scientist | analyst     | software-developer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
City: london, marseilles, nizza
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person traveling to london is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| City   | nizza | marseilles  | london  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, trike, jet-ski
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person driving the bus##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| Transport   | trike | jet-ski     | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, american, australian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the brazilian is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the american##1
3. the american is in an odd position##4
4. the australian is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | american | australian | brazilian   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, skiing, baseball
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's sport is baseball##2
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Sport   | baseball | volleyball | skiing |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, indie, house
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, snake
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the fan of blues##2
2. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | indie | house | blues |
| Pet    | rat    | frog | snake     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, funk
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, juice
1. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | dubstep  | ambient  |
| Beverage         | juice | cola | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, badminton
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| Sport       | cycling | badminton | baseball   |

