.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, colombian, nigerian
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, teacher, fisherman
1. the fisherman is on the right of the security-guard##1
2. the australian is the fisherman##1
3. the teacher is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the fisherman is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | australian |
| Job     | teacher     | security-guard   | fisherman        |

