.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, french
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, april, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the french##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is the dutch##1
3. the french is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | french  | canadian | dutch   |
| Birthday         | april | june   | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
House: farmhouse, futuristic, modern
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the modern house is between the futuristic house and the owner of the pony##2
2. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the modern house is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| House   | futuristic | modern | farmhouse |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
3 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, scrabble
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
4. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Game   | bridge  | scrabble     | backgammon |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
