2. the turkish is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the colombian is in an odd position##4
4. the american is on the left or right of the colombian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Food          | watermelon | cucumber | kale  |
| Nationality   | turkish      | american  | colombian |

