.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
3 different games are played: chess, scrabble, domino
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing chess is in the middle##1
3. the person playing domino is the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Game         | domino | chess   | scrabble |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | classical | jazz      |

