.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, plum, corn
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, thai
1. the thai is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
2. the person eating asparagus is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating plum##1
4. the person eating plum is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Food      | asparagus | plum | corn |
| Nationality   | argentine   | thai          | american |

