.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, writing, fishing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Hobby     | writing  | fishing   | board-games |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 